{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we had to give up our treasured possessions, such as jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans demanded that we give up our furs and jewelry, not that we had any furs, but we had some jewelry, especially since my father was a jeweler.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, obviously, nobody gave up everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, Jewish people are not fools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nor are other people fools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then all the schools were closed, all the businesses were closed, but there were-- then stores did open.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, there were cafes a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And culture thrived, believe it or not, in the Warsaw Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know whether or not you're aware of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was all underground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were concerts, there were readings of poetry, there was a great deal of writing, a great deal of art was produced.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Certainly in the beginning, but even later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father made sure that my sister and I received a good education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- he was not the only one-- but there were groups of children, they were called [NON-ENGLISH], which means a group of children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were five of us in the group to which I belong.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Five children, we had five teachers, and we studied in each other's homes, every day in a different house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I had--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I completed five years of elementary school before the war, and then I did the sixth grade, you know, in the clandestine school, in an underground school, and two years of gymnasium, of high school.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Learned Latin, you know, and Hebrew-- because we had a Hebrew teacher, which was great, because we had already had four years of Hebrew anyway-- and everything else.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was extremely dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
